Awayii kɛna [[Etaazuunii|Etaazunii]] ɛjaɖɛ taa tɛtʊ cikpetʊ natʊyʊ. Nɛ Etazuunii ɛjaɖɛ ɖɩnɛ ɖɩ-taa lɛ ajɛya cikpena naayɛ nɩɩnɩwa kpɛndɩna nɛ aɖʊ nɔɔ nɛ awɛɛ ɛjaɖɛ kʊɖʊmɖɩyɛ taa kpaɩ. Etaazunii tɔbʊʊ nɛ kabɩyɛ taa se ajɛya kɩkpɛndʊʊ. Awayii taa tɛtʊ sɔsɔtʊ payaɣ se Honolulu nɛ tɩ-taa ɖɔɖɔ kɛ ɛyaa kɩla ɖɔʊ.

Awayii kɛna tɛtʊ ndʊ tiɖeke tɩfɛyɩna Amerika keteŋga nɛ hayi kiŋ yɔ. Mbʊ pʊyɔɔ yɔ, ɖɩwɛna [[Oseyanii tɛtʋ wandamm|Oseyanii]] taa yeli. Ɛjaɖɛ cikpeɖe ɖɩnɛ ɖɩ-taa lɛ,tɛtʊ ñabɩ ndʊ lɩm cɔ-tʊ nɛ pɩta yɔ tɩkpɛnda 137 nɛ tɛtʊ cokolo cokolo ñɩndʊ ndʊ tɩkpɛndɩna nɛ pɩpɩsɩ Awayii ɛjaɖɛ.
